\fI500000\fR

.RE
.RE
.RS 0
.TP 8
\fBptpengine:sync_outlier_filter_stepdetect_credit [\fIINT\fB: 50 .. 1000]\fR
.RS 8
.TP 8
\fBusage\fR
Initial credit (number of samples) the Sync step detection filter can block for.
