.RS 0
.TP 8
\fBptpengine:sync_outlier_filter_stepdetect_credit_increment [\fIINT\fB: 1 .. 100]\fR
.RS 8
.TP 8
\fBusage\fR
Amount of credit for the Sync step detection filter restored every full sample window
