.RS 0
.TP 8
\fBglobal:statistics_file_max_files [\fIINT\fB: 0 .. 100]\fR
.RS 8
.TP 8
\fBusage\fR
Enable log rotation of the statistics file up to n files. 0 - do not rotate.
.TP 8
\fBdefault\fR
\fI0\fR

.RE
