.RS 0
.TP 8
\fBglobal:statistics_file_truncate [\fIBOOLEAN\fB]\fR
.RS 8
.TP 8
\fBusage\fR
Truncate the statistics file every time it is (re) opened: startup and SIGHUP.
.TP 8
\fBdefault\fR
\fIN\fR

.RE
